(626,	1,	'iPad 4 Glass/Digitizer &amp; LCD Replacement',	'iPad 4 glass is not the only thing susceptible to breaking, sometimes the LCD screen is damaged with the glass. If your iPad 4 LCD screen is non-functioning, suffering from lines across the display, or any other strange symptoms, stop by a uBreakiFix today for iPad 4 glass/LCD replacement services!',	'Are you in need of a iPad 4 Glass/Digitizer &amp; LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPad 4 Glass/Digitizer &amp; LCD Replacement!',	'',	'iPad 4 Glass/Digitizer &amp; LCD Replacement, iPad 4, Glass &amp; LCD Replacement'),
(627,	1,	'iPad 4 LCD Replacement',	'Are your experienceing a bleeding or slashed screen, cracked LCD, dead pixel(s) or an ll white or black screen on your iPad 4. If so, the iPad 4 LCD display replacement service is right for you!',	'Are you in need of a iPad 4 LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPad 4 LCD Replacement!',	'',	'iPad 4 LCD Replacement, iPad 4, LCD Replacement'),
(71,	1,	'iPhone 4S Charge Port Repair',	'Having trouble connecting your iPhone 4S to your computer, or your charger? You are not alone, iPhone 4S charge port issues are quite common. Luckily, we have the tech savvy to test and repair your iPhone 4S charge port, so you can get back to connecting to the rest of the world.',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 4S Charge Port Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 4S Charge Port Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 4S Charge Port Repair, iPhone 4S, Charge Port Repair'),
(72,	1,	'iPhone 4S White Glass &amp; LCD Replacement',	'If your white iPhone 4S front glass/LCD is less than perfect, stop by today for glass/LCD replacement! Just want to change things up with a white front, that\'s ok as well! Stop by today and you will have an iPhone 4S that looks brand new in your hands in most cases as little as 45 minutes!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 4S White Glass &amp; LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 4S White Glass &amp; LCD Replacement!',	'',	'iPhone 4S White Glass &amp; LCD Replacement, iPhone 4S, White Glass &amp; LCD Replacement'),
(73,	1,	'iPhone 4S Front Camera Repair',	'Having problems taking a selfie with your front-facing iPhone 4S camera? Bring in your iPhone 4S today for for front camera repair, so you can get back to taking selfies with confidence!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 4S Front Camera Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 4S Front Camera Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 4S Front Camera Repair, iPhone 4S, Front Camera Repair'),
(74,	1,	'iPhone 4S White Back Cover Replacement',	'Whether your iPhone 4S\'s white back cover is damaged, or you would just like to switch things up, this is the repair service for you. Stop by today for a white iPhone 4S back cover replacement, and be proud of your phone again!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 4S White Back Cover Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 4S White Back Cover Replacement!',	'',	'iPhone 4S White Back Cover Replacement, iPhone 4S, White Back Cover Replacement'),
(75,	1,	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Camera Replacement',	'Having trouble taking pictures on your At&amp;t iPhone 4? Is the camera cracked, not opening, or otherwise obscured? We can help you! Bring your iPhone in, and we will let you know exactly what your camera needs, or replace it, so you can get back to taking pictures in the blink of an eye!',	'Are you in need of a At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Camera Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Camera Replacement!',	'',	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Camera Replacement, At&amp;t iPhone 4, Camera Replacement'),
(76,	1,	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Cover Replacement',	'Is the back of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 in rough shape? Cracked, scratched, or just plain embarrasing? You don\'t have to try and hide the back of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 any longer! Visit uBreakiFix today so you can make your At&amp;t iPhone 4 brand new again, with the help of a new back cover.',	'Are you in need of a At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Cover Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Cover Replacement!',	'',	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Cover Replacement, At&amp;t iPhone 4, Back Cover Replacement'),
(77,	1,	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Battery Replacement',	'Is your At&amp;t iPhone 4 battery sleeping on the job? Not charging, not holding a charge, or dying faster than it should? Our At&amp;t iPhone 4 battery replacement service is just the thing you need! Stop in today, to see how we can get your battery back on the job!',	'Are you in need of a At&amp;t iPhone 4 Battery Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 Battery Replacement!',	'',	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Battery Replacement, At&amp;t iPhone 4, Battery Replacement'),
(78,	1,	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Charge Port Repair',	'Having trouble connecting your At&amp;t iPhone 4 to your computer, or your charger? You are not alone, At&amp;t iPhone 4 charge port issues are quite common. Luckily, we have the tech savvy to test and repair your At&amp;t iPhone 4 charge port, so you can get back to connecting to the rest of the world.',	'Are you in need of a At&amp;t iPhone 4 Charge Port Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 Charge Port Repair!',	'',	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Charge Port Repair, At&amp;t iPhone 4, Charge Port Repair'),
(79,	1,	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Ear Speaker Repair',	'Not having an ear speaker is detrimental to being able to use your At&amp;t iPhone 4!  Whether it is a fuzzy/crackling sound, sound that fades in and out or no sound, we can help you out. Bring in your At&amp;t iPhone 4 today for ear speaker repair, and get back to using your phone on the go!',	'Are you in need of a At&amp;t iPhone 4 Ear Speaker Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 Ear Speaker Repair!',	'',	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Ear Speaker Repair, At&amp;t iPhone 4, Ear Speaker Repair'),
(622,	1,	'PC Driver Install',	'Drivers that have been uninstalled or installed can cause a variety of issues on your PC. We are able to scan your PC for missing or improperly installed drivers, thus performing our PC driver install service. If you have questions about drivers, stop by uBreakiFix today!',	'Are you in need of a PC Driver Install? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC Driver Install!',	'',	'PC Driver Install, PC, Driver Install'),
(623,	1,	'PC Virus Removal',	'Viruses are the worst! Whether from browsing, dowloading, or emailing, they can wreak havoc on your PC. If you suspect you have a virus, stop by today for our PC virus removal service- remember diagnostics are always free!',	'Are you in need of a PC Virus Removal? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC Virus Removal!',	'',	'PC Virus Removal, PC, Virus Removal'),
(624,	1,	'Samsung Note 2 Glass Replacement',	'&lt;p&gt;Did your Samsung Note 2 jump out of your hand, and find itself with cracked glass? We\'ve all done it, and know how frustrating and embarrassing cracked glass can be. If your phone screen is shattered or just has one small crack, stop in today for our Samsung Note 2 glass replacement service, and stop trying to see through the cracks!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n',	'Are you in need of a Samsung Note 2 Glass Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Samsung Note 2 Glass Replacement!',	'',	'Samsung Note 2 Glass Replacement, Samsung Note 2, Glass Replacement'),
(625,	1,	'iPad 4 Glass Replacement',	'Did the glass shatter on your iPad 4? If you are tired of looking at the cracks on your iPad 4 screen, stop by today for our iPad 4 glass replacement service. You can get back to browsing, working and watching videos without the eyesore of broken glass!',	'Are you in need of a iPad 4 Glass Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPad 4 Glass Replacement!',	'',	'iPad 4 Glass Replacement, iPad 4, Glass Replacement'),
(620,	1,	'PC Charging Port',	'Is your PC not charging? D/C port broken or damaged? Let us fix it for you! Some parts may need to be special ordered. We service Samsung, HP, Dell, Toshiba, Alienware, Lenovo, Acer, and any other brand. Stop by today to have your PC looked at by a dedicated technician!',	'Are you in need of a PC Charging Port? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC Charging Port!',	'',	'PC Charging Port, PC, Charge Port Repair'),
(621,	1,	'PC OS Install',	'Whether your computer is lagging, crashing, or you just want a fresh start, consider the PC OS install service. Stop in today to see what we can do for your PC to get it optimized and working like new again!',	'Are you in need of a PC OS Install? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC OS Install!',	'',	'PC OS Install, PC, PC OS Install'),
(612,	1,	'PC Hard Drive Repair',	'Does it seem like the hard drive on your PC is acting up? Don\'t worry! We have a PC hard drive repair service that can have your hard drive on the road to recovery in no time.',	'Are you in need of a PC Hard Drive Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC Hard Drive Repair!',	'',	'PC Hard Drive Repair, PC, Hard Drive Upgrade/Replacement'),
(613,	1,	'PC Data Recovery',	'Did your hard drive die and and take vital content with it? Come in and we will track down your lost data! We service Samsung, HP, Dell, Toshiba, Alienware, Lenovo, Acer, and many other brands of PCs. If for whatever reason we are unable to recover your data, you will not be charged. Stop by uBreakiFix today to have your data recovered!',	'Are you in need of a PC Data Recovery? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC Data Recovery!',	'',	'PC Data Recovery, PC, Data Recovery'),
(614,	1,	'PC Display Replacement',	'Whether your PC display has been damaged or is just not functioning properly, we have just the repair service for you. From cracks to discoloration, we can get the display on your PC replaced in no time- stop by uBreakiFix today!',	'Are you in need of a PC Display Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC Display Replacement!',	'',	'PC Display Replacement, PC, Display Replacement'),
(615,	1,	'PC Diagnostic',	'PC acting strangely and not quite sure what the problem may be? We can put your device through our PC diagnostic services to pinpoint exactly what the issue is! Diagnostics are always free, and a technician will always contact you post-diagnostics with a repair price and wait time.',	'Are you in need of a PC Diagnostic? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC Diagnostic!',	'',	'PC Diagnostic, PC, Diagnostic Service'),
(616,	1,	'PC Memory Replacement',	'Is your PC performing at an unreasonably slow pace? Blue screen of death impending your work progress? Sounds like your PC memory could be failing. Stop by today to see if the PC memory replacement service is for you!',	'Are you in need of a PC Memory Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC Memory Replacement!',	'',	'PC Memory Replacement, PC, Memory Upgrade/Replacement'),
(618,	1,	'PC Trackpad Repair',	'Trackpads can go bad or suffer insufficient performance over time- if this sounds like you we offer a PC trackpad repair service. We can have that trackpad back to fully functioning in no time!',	'Are you in need of a PC Trackpad Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC Trackpad Repair!',	'',	'PC Trackpad Repair, PC, Trackpad Repair'),
(619,	1,	'PC Optical Drive Repair',	'Optical drive stop functioning and putting a damper on your movie watching or music listening? Stop by uBreakiFix today to see if the PC optical drive repair is for you!',	'Are you in need of a PC Optical Drive Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC Optical Drive Repair!',	'',	'PC Optical Drive Repair, PC, Optical Drive Repair'),
(617,	1,	'PC Keyboard Repair',	'PC keyboards can malfunction after liquid spills, physical damage, years of wear and tear, or issues such as dust and build-up. If your keyboard is no longer allowing you to work in the most efficient way, stop in today for our PC keyboard repair service- you\'ll be accurately typing away in no time!',	'Are you in need of a PC Keyboard Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PC Keyboard Repair!',	'',	'PC Keyboard Repair, PC, Keyboard Repair'),
(611,	1,	'Sprint/Verizon iPhone 4 Color Conversion',	'&lt;p&gt;Want to change things up with a different color Sprint/Verizon iPhone 4? Stop by today and get your Sprint/Verizon iPhone 4 convered to a unique color and looking brand new!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n',	'Are you in need of a Sprint/Verizon iPhone 4 Color Conversion? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Sprint/Verizon iPhone 4 Color Conversion!',	'',	'Sprint/Verizon iPhone 4 Color Conversion, Sprint/Verizon iPhone 4, Color Conversion'),
