(52,	1,	'iPhone 4S Battery Replacement',	'Is your iPhone 4S battery sleeping on the job? Not charging, not holding a charge, or dying faster than it should? Our iPhone 4S battery replacement service is just the thing you need! Stop in today, to see how we can get your battery back on the job!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 4S Battery Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 4S Battery Replacement!',	'',	'iPhone 4S Battery Replacement, iPhone 4S, Battery Replacement'),
