(606,	1,	'HTC Incredible 2 Glass/Touch Screen Replacement',	'If your HTC Incredible 2 is the victim of shattered glass, you don\'t have to stress any longer. We have glass replacement service for nearly any brand you can think of, and we would like to get your phone back in working order most of the time the same day!',	'Are you in need of a HTC Incredible 2 Glass/Touch Screen Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your HTC Incredible 2 Glass/Touch Screen Replacement!',	'',	'HTC Incredible 2 Glass/Touch Screen Replacement, HTC Incredible 2, Glass Replacement'),
(607,	1,	'HTC Incredible 2 LCD Replacement',	'Are your experienceing a bleeding or slashed screen, cracked LCD, dead pixel(s) or an ll white or black screen on your HTC Incredible 2. If so, the HTC Incredible 2 LCD display replacement service is right for you!',	'Are you in need of a HTC Incredible 2 LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your HTC Incredible 2 LCD Replacement!',	'',	'HTC Incredible 2 LCD Replacement, HTC Incredible 2, LCD Replacement'),
(609,	1,	'HTC Amaze Glass/Touch Screen &amp; LCD Replacement',	'Glass is not always the only thing to break on a HTC Amaze. After a drop the LCD can suffer damage as well, leading to a black screen, lines across the display or a screen that does not respond properly to touch or swipe gestures. Stop in today, and we can get your HTC Amaze started on its very own glass/LCD repair process.',	'Are you in need of a HTC Amaze Glass/Touch Screen &amp; LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your HTC Amaze Glass/Touch Screen &amp; LCD Replacement!',	'',	'HTC Amaze Glass/Touch Screen &amp; LCD Replacement, HTC Amaze, Glass &amp; LCD Replacement'),
