(448,	4,	'iPad 3 Glass/Digitizer &amp; LCD Replacement',	'iPad 3 glass is not the only thing susceptible to breaking, sometimes the LCD screen is damaged with the glass. If your iPad 3 LCD screen is non-functioning, suffering from lines across the display, or any other strange symptoms, stop by a uBreakiFix today for iPad 3 glass/LCD replacement services!',	'Are you in need of a iPad 3 Glass/Digitizer &amp; LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPad 3 Glass/Digitizer &amp; LCD Replacement!',	'',	'iPad 3 Glass/Digitizer &amp; LCD Replacement, iPad 3, Glass &amp; LCD Replacement'),
(642,	4,	'Nexus 4 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement',	'Glass is not always the only thing to break on a Nexus 4. After a drop the LCD can suffer damage as well, leading to a black screen, lines across the display or a screen that does not respond properly to touch or swipe gestures. Stop in today, and we can get your Nexus 4 started on its very own glass/LCD repair process.',	'Are you in need of a Nexus 4 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Nexus 4 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement!',	'',	'Nexus 4 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement, Nexus 4, Glass &amp; LCD Replacement'),
(643,	4,	'Samsung Galaxy S4 Glass Replacement',	'&lt;p&gt;Did your Samsung Galaxy S4 jump out of your hand, and find itself with cracked glass? We\'ve all done it, and know how frustrating and embarrassing cracked glass can be. If your phone screen is shattered or just has one small crack, stop in today for our Samsung Galaxy S4 glass replacement service, and stop trying to see through the cracks!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n',	'Are you in need of a Samsung Galaxy S4 Glass Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Samsung Galaxy S4 Glass Replacement!',	'',	'Samsung Galaxy S4 Glass Replacement, Samsung Galaxy S4, Glass Replacement'),
(644,	4,	'HTC Incredible 4G LTE Glass &amp; LCD Replacement',	'Glass is not always the only thing to break on a HTC Incredible 4G LTE. After a drop the LCD can suffer damage as well, leading to a black screen, lines across the display or a screen that does not respond properly to touch or swipe gestures. Stop in today, and we can get your HTC Incredible 4G LTE started on its very own glass/LCD repair process.',	'Are you in need of a HTC Incredible 4G LTE Glass &amp; LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your HTC Incredible 4G LTE Glass &amp; LCD Replacement!',	'',	'HTC Incredible 4G LTE Glass &amp; LCD Replacement, HTC Incredible 4G LTE, Glass &amp; LCD Replacement'),
(645,	4,	'XBOX 360 Slim Disc Drive Replacement',	'Being an XBOX 360 user, you may have experienced errors while trying to play discs. If this is the case, you need the XBOX 360 disc drive replacement service. Stop by today to see how we can prevent future disc drive errors for you in the future!',	'Are you in need of a XBOX 360 Slim Disc Drive Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your XBOX 360 Slim Disc Drive Replacement!',	'',	'XBOX 360 Slim Disc Drive Replacement, XBOX 360 Slim, Disc Drive Replacement'),
(646,	4,	'XBOX 360 Slim Disc Read Error Repair',	'Sometimes, disc drive errors in an XBOX 360 need more than a disc drive repair service. There are times when the situation does warrant an entire XBOX 360 disc drive replacement. Stop by uBreakiFix today, and a trained technician will provide you with an honest evaluation of exactly what your console needs!',	'Are you in need of a XBOX 360 Slim Disc Read Error Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your XBOX 360 Slim Disc Read Error Repair!',	'',	'XBOX 360 Slim Disc Read Error Repair, XBOX 360 Slim, Disc Read Error Repair'),
(647,	4,	'XBOX 360 Slim E74 Error Repair',	'XBOX 360s can experience a particular kind of error called an E74 error upon start-up. If your console is experiencing this issue, stop in today for our E74 error repair service. We will ensure that this issue is taken care of, and you can get back to gaming in no time!',	'Are you in need of a XBOX 360 Slim E74 Error Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your XBOX 360 Slim E74 Error Repair!',	'',	'XBOX 360 Slim E74 Error Repair, XBOX 360 Slim, E74 Error Repair'),
(648,	4,	'XBOX 360 Slim Red Ring of Death Repair',	'The Red Ring of Death is something every XBOX 360 user has heard of- and dreads. If this notorious light has made its way on to your XBOX, then stop by today for our XBOX 360 Red Ring of Death Repair service. Our technicians will make sure this light haunts you no longer, and you can get back to regular XBOX use in no time!',	'Are you in need of a XBOX 360 Slim Red Ring of Death Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your XBOX 360 Slim Red Ring of Death Repair!',	'',	'XBOX 360 Slim Red Ring of Death Repair, XBOX 360 Slim, Red Ring of Death Repair'),
(649,	4,	'PS3 Slim BluRay Drive Repair',	'Having trouble with discs in your PS3? From not ejecting or not reading discs, it can hold up your day to have a malfunctioning PS3. Stop in today to find out about our PS3 BluRay drive repair service!',	'Are you in need of a PS3 Slim BluRay Drive Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PS3 Slim BluRay Drive Repair!',	'',	'PS3 Slim BluRay Drive Repair, PS3 Slim, BluRay Drive Repair'),
(650,	4,	'PS3 Slim Flashing Red Light Repair',	'Is your PS3 displaying the flashing red light and no picture when you try to turn it on? Over time, the re-heating of the board through general use can affect the device\'s performance. Using our re-flow technique, we can get the board back to a healthy place that eliminates future PS3 red light errors.',	'Are you in need of a PS3 Slim Flashing Red Light Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PS3 Slim Flashing Red Light Repair!',	'',	'PS3 Slim Flashing Red Light Repair, PS3 Slim, Flashing Red Light Repair'),
(651,	4,	'PS3 Slim Yellow Light of Death Repair',	'Does your PS3 suffer from the \"yellow light of death\" error? What was once a source of frustration for PS3 users, is now a repair service we provide. Through a perfected process, we are able to eliminate the dreaded yellow light in no time. Stop by uBreakiFix today and let the experienced technicians repair your PS3 and get it fully operational as quickly as possible!',	'Are you in need of a PS3 Slim Yellow Light of Death Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PS3 Slim Yellow Light of Death Repair!',	'',	'PS3 Slim Yellow Light of Death Repair, PS3 Slim, Yellow Light of Death Repair'),
(652,	4,	'PS3 Slim BluRay Drive Replacement',	'Is your PS3 displaying an error while trying to read a disc? This repair service will ensure that you do not have errors in the future, by completely replacing the BluRay drive on your PS3!',	'Are you in need of a PS3 Slim BluRay Drive Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your PS3 Slim BluRay Drive Replacement!',	'',	'PS3 Slim BluRay Drive Replacement, PS3 Slim, BluRay Drive Replacement'),
