(654,	4,	'Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 7 Diagnostic',	'Is your Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 7 acting sparatically? Not charging, LCD flicker, software bugs, not connecting to wi-fi? If your Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 7 has an issue, stop by today for a free diagnostic service! A uBreakiFix highly trained technician will run a variety of tests on your Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 7, figure out what is malfunctioning and provide you with a repair quote and time estimate. Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 7 diagnostic services are always free and if the device is unrepairable for any reason, you don\'t pay anything!',	'Are you in need of a Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 7 Diagnostic? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 7 Diagnostic!',	'',	'Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 7 Diagnostic, Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 7, Diagnostic Service'),
