(675,	4,	'Samsung Gear Diagnostic',	'Is your Samsung Gear just not being itself? Turning off randomly, experiencing display, sound, or battery issues? No matter what is going on, bring your Samsung Gear in today for our free diagnostic services. We have an array of tests that we can run to see what is ailing your Samsung Gear and then we will let you know the issue before we begin repairs. You have nothing to lose with our free Samsung Gear diagnostic services!',	'Are you in need of a Samsung Gear Diagnostic? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Samsung Gear Diagnostic!',	'',	'Samsung Gear Diagnostic, Samsung Gear, Diagnostic Service'),
(694,	4,	'iPhone 5S Camera Repair',	'&lt;p&gt;Having trouble taking pictures on your iPhone 5S? Is the camera cracked, not opening, or otherwise obscured? We can help you! Bring your iPhone in, and we will let you know exactly what your camera needs, or replace it, so you can get back to taking pictures in the blink of an eye!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5S Camera Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5S Camera Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 5S Camera Repair, iPhone 5S, Camera Replacement'),
(677,	4,	'iPhone 5 Camera Repair',	'Having trouble taking pictures on your iPhone 5? Is the camera cracked, not opening, or otherwise obscured? We can help you! Bring your iPhone in, and we will let you know exactly what your camera needs, or replace it, so you can get back to taking pictures in the blink of an eye!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5 Camera Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5 Camera Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 5 Camera Repair, iPhone 5, Camera Replacement'),
(680,	4,	'iPhone 5 Ear Speaker Repair',	'Not having an ear speaker is detrimental to being able to use your iPhone 5!  Whether it is a fuzzy/crackling sound, sound that fades in and out or no sound, we can help you out. Bring in your iPhone 5 today for ear speaker repair, and get back to using your phone on the go!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5 Ear Speaker Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5 Ear Speaker Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 5 Ear Speaker Repair, iPhone 5, Ear Speaker Repair'),
(683,	4,	'iPhone 5 Loudspeaker Repair',	'Having sound troubles with your iPhone 5 loudspeaker? Not to worry! We offer loudspeaker repair service, so you can get back to blasting music or talking on speaker phone again as fast as possible!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5 Loudspeaker Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5 Loudspeaker Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 5 Loudspeaker Repair, iPhone 5, Loudspeaker Repair'),
(684,	4,	'iPhone 5 Microphone Repair',	'Is your iPhone 5 microphone not working? This function can affect both phone conversations, voice control, and recordings, don\'t wait another minute to have your iPhone 5 microphone repaired!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5 Microphone Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5 Microphone Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 5 Microphone Repair, iPhone 5, Microphone Repair'),
(686,	4,	'iPhone 5 Volume Button Repair',	'iPhone 5 volume buttons can get stuck, fall off, or stop working altogether. If you cannot adjust your iPhone 5\'s volume at will, stop in today to get repaired by our team of dedicated professionals!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5 Volume Button Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5 Volume Button Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 5 Volume Button Repair, iPhone 5, Volume Button Repair'),
(678,	4,	'iPhone 5 Battery Replacement',	'Is your iPhone 5 battery sleeping on the job? Not charging, not holding a charge, or dying faster than it should? Our iPhone 5 battery replacement service is just the thing you need! Stop in today, to see how we can get your battery back on the job!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5 Battery Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5 Battery Replacement!',	'',	'iPhone 5 Battery Replacement, iPhone 5, Battery Replacement'),
(679,	4,	'iPhone 5 Charge Port Repair',	'Having trouble connecting your iPhone 5 to your computer, or your charger? You are not alone, iPhone 5 charge port issues are quite common. Luckily, we have the tech savvy to test and repair your iPhone 5 charge port, so you can get back to connecting to the rest of the world.',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5 Charge Port Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5 Charge Port Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 5 Charge Port Repair, iPhone 5, Charge Port Repair'),
(681,	4,	'iPhone 5 Headphone Jack Repair',	'Is your iPhone 5 only playing out of one side of your ear buds? Not playing sound at all out of headphones? Whether your headphones don\'t seem to connect, or they are no longer reliable, you can trust us to get your iPhone 5 headphone jack repaired and working like new!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5 Headphone Jack Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5 Headphone Jack Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 5 Headphone Jack Repair, iPhone 5, Headphone Jack Repair'),
(685,	4,	'iPhone 5 Power Button Repair',	'iPhone 5 power button issues are a hassle. If your power button is letting you down, stop in today for our iPhone 5 power button repair service.',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5 Power Button Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5 Power Button Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 5 Power Button Repair, iPhone 5, Power Button Repair'),
